---
description: avoid accidental paid eval runs
globs:
  - "**/*"
alwaysApply: true
---

- `bun run test:e2e`, `bun run test:e2e:all`, `bun run test:evals`, and `bun run test:evals:all` are paid/costed workflows.
- Before paid evals, run `bun run eval:select` to preview scope.
- Require explicit user confirmation before running paid evals.
- Remind that `ANTHROPIC_API_KEY` is required for `test:evals`.
